="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ListItem"><a itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing" itemprop="item" href="https://www.courrierinternational.com/infographie"><span itemprop="name">Infographie</span></a><meta itemprop="position" content="1" /></li><li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ListItem"><a itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing" itemprop="item" href="https://www.courrierinternational.com/notule-source/courrier-international"><span itemprop="name">Courrier international - Paris</span></a><meta itemprop="position" content="2" /></li></ul> <span class="date">Publié le <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2015-12-09T17:52:38+01:00">09/12/2015 - 17:52</time></span><meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2015-12-10T09:00:21+01:00"></div><p class="article-lede" itemprop="description">D’après la Global Terrorism Database, c’est en Irak que le terrorisme a fait le plus de morts depuis 2001. Cinq autres pays sont particulièrement touchés : l’Afghanistan, le Pakistan, le Nigeria, l’Inde et la Syrie.</p> <aside class="article-aside"><div class="gptcontainer"><div id="pave_haut" class="dfp-slot dfp-unloaded" data-format="pave_haut" aria-hidden="true"></div></div> <aside class="view view-ci-service-article view-id-ci_service_article view-display-id-right_service_eva view-dom-id-dbb4b7c9746d9c3536d85838aae2e645 ci-services"><div class="title-section">Nos services</div><ul class="services-list service-carousel slider-list"><li class="list-item"><div class="item"> <a href="https://www.courrierinternational.com/jeu/quiz-anglais-2020?utm_source=site-courrier&utm_medium=cta-400x260-quiz-ang&utm_campaign=202002-ag-ci-partner-gymglish"><div class="wrap"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-srcset="https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci_master/files/styles/image_235/public/marketing/400x260-quiz-anglais.jpg?itok=YfVGsawN 380w, https://www.courrierinternational.com/sites/ci